Key Match Events: Brahim Diaz scored the winning goal in the 93rd minute of stoppage time.
Pre-Game Insights: Walid Regragui opted for a comprehensive reshuffle of the starting lineup following the victory against Gabon (4-0).
Post-Match Reflections: Ayoub El Kaabi nearly scored in the first half but failed to convert a corner kick opportunity in the 39th minute. Abdessamad Ezzalzouli also missed an open goal in the second half of the match (63rd minute).
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match took place at the Adrar Stadium in Agadir.
